T02TD2558E:22b-1: 'khor ba las yid byung ba ni de bzhin du nang bcud kyi sems can dang /
T02TD2558E:22b-2: bdag gi gzugs kyi phung po yang spyi bo nas rkang pa'i mthil yan chad du brtags pas mi gtsang ba'i ngo bo yin te /
T02TD2558E:22b-9: keng rus la sogs pas yongs su gang ba /
T02TD2558E:22b-11: de yang yid brtan du mi rung pa /
T02TD2558E:22b-13: mi rtag pa bdag med pa /
T02TD2558E:22b-15: de lta bur shes par byas nas gzung 'dzin gnyis las log ste /
T02TD2558E:22b-16: sems kyi mtshan nyid kyang gzugs med pa /
T02TD2558E:22b-17: kha dog med pa ngo bo med pa /
T02TD2558E:22b-18: rnam pa med pa bltar med pa /
T02TD2558E:23a-0: gzung du med pa rtog pa @23a * //
T02TD2558E:23a-3: kun nas nyon mongs pa med pa /
T02TD2558E:23a-4: rang rig pa rang gsal ba tsam du yang grub pa yin te /
T02TD2558E:23a-5: de ltar na 'khor ba na 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la chags pa ni slu pa'i chos can yin no //
T02TD2558E:23a-6: 'khor ba las yid byung ba 'di yang rang bzo ma yin te /
T02TD2558E:23a-7: lus me lus te lus kyi mchog /
T02TD2558E:23a-8: lus kyi mtha' ni rtogs pa po //
T02TD2558E:23a-10: 'khor ba'i pha rol mthar son pa //
T02TD2558E:23a-11: bya ba byas pa skam sar gnas //
T02TD2558E:23a-12: zhes pa'i bka' rgyud la brten nas byas so //
T02TD2558E:23a-13: mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i mi rtag pa 'khor ba las yid byung ba /
T02TD2558E:23a-14: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
